body:
brighter • a social media au

part 1: I’m done with those

In which Y/N is a young history of arts student, part-time model, that every year spends her holidays with her squad in a small village in the mountains. Kim Seokjin is the most famous idol in the world and he used to come to the village too before becoming a global superstar. It has been 6 years since he visited and he suddenly came back shutting the world out. How will Y/N act around her favourite idol and long time crush?

warnings: slight cursing, mostly crack

title: bts reaction: finding their innocent friends condoms
body:
↳ waow thank you lovely human. Hope this is ok! ♡♡

(also i think ill have the time to make another reaction tomorrow so look out for that!)

Seokjin

- NONONONONONONNO

He would be so confused and shocked and surprised and question his entire life. You were the last person he’d expect to have a pretty large collection of condoms. You squirmed every time the subject of sex came up and acted like you knew nothing. 

- (Y/N) WHAT IS THIS.

- Better safe than sorry.

- WH- WHAT?! 

Namjoon

Suddenly way too curious about your love life. Almost a little invasive. He would be so intrigued because you never seemed like the sexually active type. His main goal would be to find out who the lucky person you were messing around with was.

- HEEY WASSSAP?

- Joon?! You can’t just burst into my apartment like that!

- Are you alone? Oh… I thought-… Nothing.

lil creep

Yoongi

Being the super protective brother-like best friend he would be kind of salty, wondering if the person you were seeing was good enough for you. Also he would be a little peeved that you didn’t tell him about your… love life.

- So who is he?

- I’m not telling you Yoongi.

- What? Why?

- Because you’ll talk to him and scare him off!

- *gif* Ok if I promise that I won’t, can I meet him?

Hoseok

He would be digging in your drawers to retrieve a shirt you stole from him when he found a pack of magnums. Not knowing wtf to say he would just slowly turn around and show it to Namjoon. The little devil on his shoulder would tell him to yell for everyone to come over so he can hype this up but thankfully Joon was there to reason with him.

- Is this what I think it is?

- Hoseok… you better keep quiet.

- Are you kidding? This is huge, we’ve gotta tell the others!

- Yea they are huge but she obviously hid them for a reason! Now put them back you imbecile.

did everyone get that lol im dying im so fkn funny

Jimin

Perv-mode activated!

He would not let that shit go. This boi would follow you around asking you about favorite positions, weirdest places etc. and he would not let up until he got an answer. He would probably want to know so much because he’d never had a girl to talk about this stuff with before.

- Pleaaaase tell me? I’ll tell you mine!

- Ok fine I’ll tell you. But only if you tell me yours first.

- Hmm… deal. My weirdest place is… probably a public restroom.

- Ew Jimin that’s nasty.

- Your turn! 

- Nope.

- eXSCuse mE?

Taehyung

When dinner was finished you pulled out a pack of gum from your purse and didn’t realize the condom stuck to the back of it. Taehyung saw it and it took him a solid minute to process what it actually was. He didn’t know how to bring it up but damn did he want to question you about it, hoping for a “wow i didn’t even know that was in there woopsi!”. When the bill was paid he couldn’t hold it in any longer.

- SO Whos the guy your DOING IT WITH HUH?

- what?

- I mean… I’m sorry I saw that you had condoms in your bag.

- Tae. First of all, it’s just one condom, not condoms. Second, it’s just in case, theres no guy and theres no “doing it.”. But now I know not to tell you in the future.

- Phew, I freaked out there for a sec- wait nonono you HAVE to tell me!!!!

Jungkook

He would blackmail you so hard. He was snooping in your room when he found the pretty decent amout of condoms you had in your nightstand. His first thought would be to tease the shit out of you. But that slowly changed when he realized this was perfect blackmail material. It was near impossible for him to buy his own condoms, in fear of getting noticed by the public, and also he was too shy to ask his hyungs, so this was perfect.

- Hey (Y/N). I found your little stash.

- Excuse me?

- Look. This can either go smoothly without anybody finding out or I will blast the fact that you have condoms in the groupchat.

- *dramatic gasph* What do you want?

- I get to take some whenever I need to. 

- Fine.

- And next time you get to pick what we eat for dinner, you pick pizza.

- You monster… fine.

- Are you alone? Oh… I thought-… Nothing.

did everyone get that lol im dying im so fkn funny

Jimin

He didn’t know how to bring it up but damn did he want to question you about it, hoping for a “wow i didn’t even know that was in there woopsi!”. When the bill was paid he couldn’t hold it in any longer.

It was near impossible for him to buy his own condoms, in fear of getting noticed by the public, and also he was too shy to ask his hyungs, so this was perfect.
